<h3>How Many Links Do You Need?</h3>
<p>The answer depends on your competitive space. Use <a href="/blog/seo-competitor-analysis/">competitor analysis</a> to benchmark:</p>
<ol>
<li>Identify 3-5 direct competitors ranking for your target keywords</li>
<li>Check their referring domain count using <a href="/reviews/ahrefs/">Ahrefs</a> or <a href="/reviews/semrush/">Semrush</a></li>
<li>Calculate the gap between your domain and theirs</li>
<li>Target closing 10-20% of that gap per quarter</li>
</ol>
<p>A SaaS site with 50 referring domains competing against sites with 500+ needs a multi-year link building strategy. There are no shortcuts.</p>
